a bag. Air dry in a shady spot.</p>","default_open_accordion":false}},"a34f6081-2778-463c-8074-6403bf19be80":{"type":"accordion_content","settings":{"section_class":"section_class","page":"","title":"Shipping, Returns & Warranty","text":"<p>SHIPPING</p><p>Worldwide<strong> </strong>shipping from Bali & Australia. Free EXPRESS Shipping for orders $250+ AUD.</p><p>International Express Shipping will be sent via DHL and will arrive in 2 - 4 days once dispatched.</p><p>Domestic Indonesian & Australian orders will be sent express and arrive in 1 - 3 days.</p><p>Please read more of our Shipping Policy <a href=\"/policies/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">here.</a></p><p>RETURNS/EXCHANGES</p><p>We accept exchanges or returns for change of mind for a credit note, on full price items only, and as long as it is processed within within 30 days from the date the item was dispatched.<br/></p><p>Sale items cannot be exchanged or refunded.</p><p>Please follow instructions on our  <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\">Returns </a>page.</p><p>WARRANTY</p><p>We stand by the quality of our swimsuits, they are tailor made with high quality Italian fabric. </p><p>We offer a 12 month warranty from date of purchase, shall the make, material or hardware malfunction.</p><p>Read more about our warranty <a href=\"/pages/warranty\" title=\"Warranty\">here.</a></p>","default_open_accordion":false}},"0c52e621-4467-4df7-9a79-186536b36b30":{"type":"accordion_content","settings":{"section_class":"section_class","page":"","title":"Contact Us","text":"<p>Have a question? You can reach us below or on live chat.</p><p><a href=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"http://wa.me/61407215854\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://wa.me/61407215854\">Whats App</a></p><p></p>","default_open_accordion":false}},"f2eafac5-